        "bullet_point": [
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "High Stability and Safety: Electric Jack has a heavy-duty steel construction, large base and saddle make this car jack strong and stable. Due to the safety compact design, jack will automatically stop working when it reaches the height limitation. Size Of The Product - Electric Jack - 38Cm X 15Cm , Electric Wrench - 26Cm X 14Cm",
            "marketplace_id": "A21TJRUUN4KGV"
          },
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "Two-way Power Supply: Scissor Lift Jack can be connected to either a 12 V outlet or car battery, two connector choices make it a necessary car tool kit when run into roadside emergencies",
            "marketplace_id": "A21TJRUUN4KGV"
          },
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "High Efficiency: Floor Jack takes as short as 2 min to reach maximum height (30 to 37cm) with loading capacity as high as 3T and easily lift your vehicle off the ground. The wrench works effectively with about 5 seconds to remove the nut. Perfect match for car repair and emergency use.",
            "marketplace_id": "A21TJRUUN4KGV"
          },
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "Designed for Suv, Sedan: Car Repair Tool has two removable raised heads are respectively designed for Sedan and SUV, with two non-slip silicone sleeves, which can prevent sliding between vehicle and jack during the lifting process, to ensure safer operation. Vehicles under 2 ton can be easily lifted, but DO NOT use it on the trucks and those beyond 2 ton.",
            "marketplace_id": "A21TJRUUN4KGV"
          },
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "The box includes: Electric car jack x 1, Battery clip x 1, Cigarette lighter power line x 1, Fuse x 3 (15A), Hand crank x 1, Electric car wrench x 1, Double sockets (17/19mm, 21/23mm) and 6months manufacturing defect warranty.",
