        "product_description": [
          {
            "language_tag": "en_IN",
            "value": "<p>BKR 2 in 1 Hydraulic Electric Car Jack 141215 The electronic jack can lift up to 5-ton weight and is with a fashionable and beautiful design, and adopt the advance electric machinery technology. It's a must-have product for your car for effortless tire replacement. </p> <p>INSTRUCTION FOR CAR JACK:</p> <li>When replacing the tyre in an emergent time, turn on the caution light, put the car in a level place (no more than 6 degrees), pull the controller, and use tyre cushion or other anti skit material to keep the tyre to be stable, ensure the vehicle already safety arrestment.</li> <li> The electric car jack is connected to the 12V power supply by the following ways, CIGARETTE LIGHTER CONNECTED: Connect on eside of the cigarette lighter power line with the vehicle cigarette lighter, the other put into the remote control socket of an electric car jack. (ATTENTION: THE RATED CURRENT OF CIGARETTE LIGHTER FUSE NO LESS THAN 12A). Vehicle battery direct connected: When the current of cigarette lighter fuse less than 12A. connect the clip, red clip with the mark \"+\", black with \"-\", the other side connected with remote control handle socket.</li><li>Choose the stable car jack support points, and rotate it to the top round hole.</li><li>Accordingto the instructions provided by the automaker, the top of the jack is aligned to the appropriate position of the vehicle at the bottom. (Usually is placed on the steel beam near the replaced tyre.</li>Press the button \"^\" on the remote control to lifting the vehicle until the tyre leave the ground.</li><li>When the car is well repaired, press the button \"V\" on the remote control decline to the beginning state.</li>",
            "marketplace_id": "A21TJRUUN4KGV"
          }
        ],
